Pizza shop 

Write an application for managing the menu for a pizza shop.
A Pizza has an id:Long (entity identifier), 
name:String, description:String, price:float. The name is unique.
When visiting the address
 http://localhost:4200/pizzashop/pizzas a Load button is shown only. When pressing the button, at the same address:
- 
the list of pizzas is shown (pizza name only)
When clicking on a pizza, at the same address, the following text is 
shown below the list of pizzas in one label:
description: <pizza description>
price: <pizza price>

Nonfunctional 
requirements:
You will have to use the technologies, architecture, style etc from the labs
On the backend all 
operations will be logged (as done at the labs)
Use proper identifiers - related to this problem only

